com.cognifide.qa.bb.scope.nested

Class ScopedElementLocator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cognifide.qa.bb.scope.nested.ScopedElementLocator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openqa.selenium.support.pagefactory.ElementLocator

    public class ScopedElementLocator
extends Object
implements org.openqa.selenium.support.pagefactory.ElementLocator
    This is a two-step locator. First it constructs a scope out of the scope factory and the parent field, then searches for the injected field in this scope.
